{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make it illegal for a child to be left home alone before a specific age",
        "additional_details": "I'm concerned this means people's judgement is used which could be poor. I think it is frightening that people are able to use their own judgment in these situations.",
        "background": "We want the government to make it illegal for a child to be left home alone before a specific, appropriate age and consequences for parents found breaking the law. Currently the law does not say a specific age when a child can be left on their own.",
